Package us.ullberg.startpunkt.crd.v1alpha4

Class BookmarkSpec

java.lang.Object
us.ullberg.startpunkt.crd.v1alpha4.BookmarkSpec
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<BookmarkSpec>
public class BookmarkSpec extends Object implements Comparable<BookmarkSpec>
Represents the specification of a Bookmark custom resource. Includes properties such as name, group, icon, URL, info, target behavior, and sorting location.
